        "title": "金牛座εb",
        "content": "{{Infobox Planet\n| bgcolour = #A0B0FF\n| image =\n| caption =\n| name = 金牛座ε星b\n| parent star = yes\n| star = 金牛座ε星\n| planet = \n| constell = 金牛座\n| distance = 155 ± 6光年\n| RA = {{RA|04|28|37.0}}\n| DEC = {{DEC|+19|10|49}}\n| class = K0III\n| discovery = yes\n| discovery_ref = \n| discoverer = 佐藤文衛等人\n| discovered = 2007年2月7日\n| discovery_method = 多普勒光谱法\n| semimajor = 1.93 ± 0.03天文单位\n| semiminor = \n| orbital_circ = \n| eccentricity = 0.151 ± 0.023\n| period = 645.5 ± 5.3地球日\n| inclination = \n| long_periastron = 94.4 ± 7.4°\n| time_periastron = 2,452,879 ± 12儒略日\n| semi-amp = 98.5 ± 1.8m/s\n| physical_characteristics = yes\n| mean_radius = \n| density = \n| surface_grav = \n| mass = \n| minimum_mass = 7.6 ± 0.2倍木星质量\n| single_temperature = \n| magnitude =\n}}\n'''金牛座ε星b'''是一颗位于[[金牛座]]、距离地球约155光年的系外行星。其母星为[[金牛座ε]]，是[[毕宿星团]]六颗巨星之一，其质量为[[太阳]]的2.7倍，这使其成为迄今为止发现的拥有行星的质量最大的恒星，该恒星在其[[主序星]]阶段可能是一颗A型恒星。金牛座ε星b的轨道与其母星的距离要比地球轨道和太阳的距离大，其轨道离心率适中。\n\n现今还不知晓该行星的轨道倾角。有些科学家认为金牛座ε星b也可能是一颗[[褐矮星]]。\n\n==参考文献==\n* {{cite journal |url=http://oklo.org/?p=188 |author=Sato et al. |title=Lonely Planet Guide to Hyades |work=Systemic |year=2007 |volume= |pages= |access-date=2009-06-11 |archive-date=2008-12-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081216152714/http://oklo.org/?p=188 |dead-url=no }}\n* {{cite journal |url=http://www.centauri-dreams.org/?p=1071 |author=Sato et al. |title=Hyades Planet Challenges Formation Theories |work=Centauri Dreams |year=2007 |volume= |pages= |access-date=2009-06-11 |archive-date=2017-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170118142700/http://www.centauri-dreams.org/?p=1071 |dead-url=no }}\n\n==外部链接==\n* {{cite web |url=http://exoplanet.eu/planet.php?p1=eps+Tau&p2=b |title=Notes for planet eps Tau b |accessdate=2008-06-24 |work=The Extrasolar Planets Encyclopaedia |archive-date=2010-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100407175901/http://exoplanet.eu/planet.php?p1=eps+Tau&p2=b |dead-url=no }}\n{{-}}\n{{extrasolar-planet-stub}}\n{{Sky|04|28|37.0|+|19|10|49|155}}\n[[Category:太阳系外行星]]\n[[Category:金牛座]]\n[[Category:类木行星]]\n[[Category:2007年发现的系外行星]]"
