        "title": "子宫旁组织炎",
        "content": "{{Infobox_Disease |\n  Name           = 子宫旁组织炎 |\n  Image          = |\n  Caption        = |\n  DiseasesDB     = |\n  ICD10          = {{ICD10|N|73|0|n|70}}-{{ICD10|N|73|2|n|70}} |\n  ICD9           = {{ICD9|614.4}} |\n  ICDO           = |\n  OMIM           = |\n  MedlinePlus    = |\n  eMedicineSubj  = |\n  eMedicineTopic = |\n  MeshID         = D010249 |\n}}{{medical}}\n'''子宫旁组织炎'''（{{lang|en|Parametritis}}），是一类[[子宫旁组织]]的[[炎症]]，病发于[[子宫]]旁的[[结缔组织]]。\n\n它是一类盆腔炎[[盆腔炎]]<ref name=\"urlBroad Ligament Disorders: eMedicine Obstetrics and Gynecology\">{{cite web |url=http://emedicine.medscape.com/article/275773-overview |title=Broad Ligament Disorders: eMedicine Obstetrics and Gynecology |format= |work= |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2019-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511085320/https://emedicine.medscape.com/article/275773-overview |dead-url=no }}</ref>。它病发于子宫旁的结缔组织，与病发生于子宫浆膜的子宫外膜炎不同。\n\n==参考==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{disease-stub}}\n{{女性盆腔和生殖器疾病}}\n{{Inflammation}}\n\n[[Category:妇科疾病]]"
